| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4710 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 49ec9abf-c385-5c14-9557-2bfeaf6fe0c8"
